Metadata-Version: 2.1
Name: git-status
Version: 0.0.2
Summary: 'git status' python wrapper
Home-page: https://github.com/looking-for-a-job/git-status.py
License: UNKNOWN
Description: [![](https://img.shields.io/pypi/pyversions/git-status.svg?longCache=True)](https://pypi.org/pypi/git-status/)
        
        ### Install
        ```bash
        $ [sudo] pip install git-status
        ```
        
        ### Examples
        `git status -s` output
        ```python
        >>> import git_status
        >>> git_status.get(".")
         M  path/to/modified
         A  path/to/added
         D  path/to/deleted
         R  path/to/renamed
         ?? path/to/untracked
        ```
        
        `Status` class
        ```python
        >>> status = git_status.Status(".")
        >>> status.A
        ['path/to/added']
        
        >>> status.M
        ['path/to/modified']
        
        >>> status.D
        ['path/to/deleted']
        
        >>> status.R
        ['path/to/renamed']
        
        >>> status.untracked
        ['path/to/untracked']
        ```
